The business lacks a structured and data-driven approach to monitor and analyze pizza sales performance across different dimensions such as time, category, size, and individual products. Without clear visibility into key metrics like revenue, order volume, and customer preferences, it becomes difficult to identify sales trends, top-performing items, and underperforming areas.
This creates challenges in understanding seasonal patterns, optimizing product strategy, and making informed business decisions. Therefore, there is a need for an interactive dashboard that consolidates sales data and provides actionable insights to improve overall performance.
